Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交友纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend-iversary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交友纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend-iversary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交友纪念日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy friend-iversary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,890)}当晚
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他全都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He remembers everything
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切发生过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything that happened
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连没发生过的事都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even things that didn't happen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后会发生的事可能也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe even things that will happen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能发生的事还能记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Things that will never happen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凡是他记得的事都会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he remembers it, it happens
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要镇静  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get ahold of yourself, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定有办法能脱身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be a way out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定有办法能消除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be a way to erase
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要擦掉他对我的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll erase his memories of me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.36,0:06:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有唯一一个存放回忆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one more place he keeps his memories
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Erase me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Erase me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我们来当室友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward, let's be roommates
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子住在一起到永远永远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and live together forever and ever and ever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定是新来的收银员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be the new cashier
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们先前见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不我们等会再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can chat later, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在有点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of busy right now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我一生最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the best day of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天莫名高兴得有点怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You seem weirdly happy for some reason
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.12,0:07:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Last night
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.95,0:07:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我消除了海绵宝宝对我的所有回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I erased all of SpongeBob's memories of me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you insane, man?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了避免痞老板扫描我意识
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To keep Plankton from scanning me mind
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有海绵宝宝才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is the only one who knows
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.09,0:08:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方保险箱的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the combination to the secret formula safe
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由于海绵宝宝不想忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And because he never wanted to forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.82,0:08:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就把密码附在跟你一起的回忆之上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ha attached it to a memory he had with you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.57,0:08:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你马上复原他的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to un-erase his memory right now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来跟章鱼哥先生共度下午时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spend the afternoon with Mr. Squidward here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.42,0:08:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要跟你分享几个宝贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's gonna share some precious memories with you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说个悄悄话  感觉他有点无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Confidentially, he looks a little boring
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟他一块走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go with him
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's an order
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们要干什么  新同事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what are we doing now, new guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重新制造出你对我失去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to recreate your lost memories of me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.70,0:08:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你想起来蟹老板保险箱的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can remember the combination of Krabs' safe
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就很扯  不过也行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds crazy-pants, but okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do what I tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:45.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,366)}泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:10:02.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986,826)}利马豆
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.82,0:10:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  要是这都没法让你想起我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, if this doesn't make you remember me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就彻底没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then nothing will
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,基本没什么印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's just not ringing a
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I remember this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想起你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想起保险箱的密码了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember the combination to the safe
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁  万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray, hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray-ay-ay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's great
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别摇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just stop shaking the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:38.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1274,778)}更烫的岩浆
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.56,0:10:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,密码是  向右三次撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The combination is three impacts to the right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.66,0:10:45.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:45.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的身子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My body
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向左打五拳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five punchings to the left
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向右拉六肢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six stretched limbs to the right
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向左56个小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And 56 school children to the left
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1392,582)}裤头村学校
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,57
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,57
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1414,975)}章鱼哥  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1414,1030)}Squidward, I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1414,975)}我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1414,1030)}I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,418)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又想起一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's something else I remembered
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨天不是我们的交友纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yesterday wasn't our friend-iversary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's today
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.65,0:11:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.15,0:11:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交友纪念日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy friend-iversary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是明天来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or is it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.76,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强制音乐课
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:46.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(704,374)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(696,678)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(634,468)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(776,662)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(746,532)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(582,538)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.09,0:12:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来欣赏动听的免费音乐会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:12:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gather round for a free concert of beautiful music
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费音乐会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A free concert
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a one, and a two
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快带我走吧  查德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here, Chad
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒犯到我耳朵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My ears are offended
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.34,0:12:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put me down
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放开我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go of my legs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My clarinet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(344,440)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.84,0:12:55.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一群俗人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:55.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Philistines
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,254)}健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再  来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, more time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许动  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freeze, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.35,0:13:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢慢把竖笛放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put the clarinet down nice and slow
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们算老几啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐警察吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The music police?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, fella
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你违反了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you are in violation of
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交响乐法典第四款
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,section four of the symphony code
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206,510)}违法
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粗鲁吹奏簧鸣乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reckless playing of a reed instrument
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.95,0:13:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的竖笛现已正式停用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your clarinet is officially out of commission
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你想要打开竖笛上的锁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want that boot off your clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.12,0:14:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须去上强制音乐再教育课程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll have to undergo mandatory music reeducation
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to be kidding me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小脚蹼音乐学院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little Flipper Music Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(912,792)}小脚蹼音乐学院
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.10,0:14:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不上小屁孩才上的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not going to any school for minnows
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能就这样给我降级
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't degrade me like this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what they all say
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼叫38号警卫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calling Guard 38
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.50,0:14:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有鼓手在比博普路的爵士俱乐部漏拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a drummer missed a beat at the jazz club on Bebop Way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家摇滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's rock and roll
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不可能坐在班级前排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be caught dead sitting in front of this class
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐在后面就看不到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They won't see me back here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, class
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.90,0:14:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家把椅子转过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would everyone please turn their chairs around?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  鲟老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ms. Sturgeon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.31,0:15:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For Neptune's sake
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子今天有位新同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like we have a new student
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.62,0:15:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就坐在我们前排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sitting right up front today
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你起立向全班自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you stand and introduce yourself to the class?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名字是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吹竖笛的年头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I've been playing clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比你们的年纪还要久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,longer than you all have been alive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么来这上课呢  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you here, Mr. Tentacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法院命令我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because of a court order
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法院命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Court order?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥有法院命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward got a court order
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥有法院命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward got a court order
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, settle down, class
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.76,0:15:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今天还有一位新同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have one more new student joining us today
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm really looking forward to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.15,0:15:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我都不知道你也来上这门课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I didn't know you were taking this class too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太美好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this wonderful?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一起学音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're musical classmates
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kill me now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  请所有同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To begin, I would like each of you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演奏一下手上的乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to play your instrument
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摸一下大家的底
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to gauge everyone's skill level
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有同学一个一个来演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll go around the classroom one by one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.59,0:16:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,费格斯  你先开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fergus, would you start us off?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  费格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good effort, Fergus
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nellie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,技巧挺有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Interesting technique
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.90,0:16:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奥托  稍微弹一弹肩背式键盘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Otto, would you play a little on your key-tar?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进步空间很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Definitely room for improvement
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Student SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给大家鉴赏一下你的音乐才能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would you give us a taste of your musical talents?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Certainly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.84,0:17:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻笛技术很棒  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent nose flute technique, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在有请章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向大家展示音乐才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to demonstrate his musical abilities
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来向你们展示真正的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let me show you how it's really done
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brace yourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.22,0:17:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们即将看到纯粹的天才之作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for you are about to witness a stroke of pure genius
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.38,0:18:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来你确实有点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It did sound like you had some kind of stroke
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竖笛对你这样的水平来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The clarinet may be too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能还是太过深奥了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,advanced for your level, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你应该试试别的乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should try a different instrument
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你应该多练练指法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should just work on your fingering
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受不了你们闹来闹去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.10,0:19:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉响音乐警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must pull music alarm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1346,826)}音乐警报
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放下竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,put down the clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,避免伤害他人的耳膜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before someone's eardrums get hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来拿啊  条子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come and take it, copper
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他力量太强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's getting too powerful
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.87,0:20:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派遣指挥名家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Send in the maestro
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.50,0:20:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闹够了吧  贝多粪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun's over, bad-toven
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up top
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你再也没法用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be hurting
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伤害到任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,anyone with this anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吹出邪恶颤音的日子结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your villainous vibrato days are over
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.70,0:21:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也演奏不出音乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never play music again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以培养新的爱好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can take up a new hobby
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.82,0:21:14.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说排绒毛或者拇指大战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:14.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like lint sorting or competitive thumb twiddling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我压根没拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have any thumbs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.64,0:21:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸巾给你擤  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and give it a big blow, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sound
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个天籁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Positively angelic
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续擤  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep going, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你终于找到适合你的乐器了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You finally found your instrument
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直都近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was right in front of your nose all along
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.92,0:21:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实就是你鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, it was your nose
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想大家都能认可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we can all agree
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.40,0:22:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生是全班进步最大的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:22:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tentacles is the most improved student in the class
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.32,0:22:14.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太有才了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:14.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a talent
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Encore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.39,0:22:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Encore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.66,0:22:19.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好样的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:19.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Encore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Encore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.18,0:22:21.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:21.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Encore
